-> 'FeedbackForm' cannot be used as a JSX component.
  Its type '(onSubmit: any, movie_id: any) => Element' is not a valid JSX element type.
    Type '(onSubmit: any, movie_id: any) => Element' is not assignable to type '(props: any) => ReactNode | Promise<ReactNode>'.
      Target signature provides too few arguments. Expected 2 or more, but got 1.